#!/usr/bin/env ruby
=begin

Simple Mailer provides a quick and easy way to send emails
from the command line, without having to install a package
that brings in postfix (I'm looking at you, bsd-mailx and 
mailutils!!).

Author:: Tamara Temple <tamara@tamaratemple.com>
Copyright:: Tamara Temple Web Development
License:: MIT

=end

require 'simplemailer'
SimpleMailer.run
